WEBVTT

00:00.374 --> 00:02.672
Previously on
<i>Falling Skies...</i>

00:02.866 --> 00:04.971
Oppression is in your nature.

00:04.997 --> 00:07.970
And <i>that</i> is your justification
for the murder of billions?

00:08.717 --> 00:10.730
What the hell
happened here?

00:10.755 --> 00:12.864
So these bastards
are shooting each other now?

00:14.156 --> 00:15.302
Maggie...

00:15.327 --> 00:16.641
Don't.

00:17.262 --> 00:18.660
In the harnessing
facility...

00:18.685 --> 00:20.413
I saw your spikes glow.

00:20.438 --> 00:21.936
You can rat me out
if you want,

00:21.961 --> 00:24.585
but I am not signing
my own death warrant.

00:24.610 --> 00:26.305
I hope you're not afraid.

00:26.330 --> 00:28.294
Whatever you think
they've done to me,

00:28.319 --> 00:29.444
I'm still Karen.

